@{!</UL>}
@endnode

@node needs "Requirements"
@{!</PRE>}@{!<UL>}
@{!<LI>}- OS 2.04 or above
@{!<LI>}- @{"MUI" link mui} (I use 3.6, dunno what version my prog needs) for the GUI - @{b}IT WILL STILL WORK WITHOUT MUI@{ub}, you just wont have a nice GUI :(
@{!</UL>}

Tested on:@{!<P>}

My Amiga 1200 with Blizzard 030iv (50MHz) board, 16 meg fast@{!<BR>}
Softkicked OS 3.1 (40.68)@{!<BR>}
MUI 3.6

@endnode

@node mui "Why MUI?"
@{!</PRE>}Simply: Its easy to code GUI's in MUI, its hard otherwise, and I like it, it looks good.@{!<P>}
Anyway, on my machine its not slow :)
@endnode

